{"title":"民兵赞（三首）","authors":["王石祥"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"民兵赞（三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军上等兵　王石祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤凰山上落凤凰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤凰山上落凤凰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘练武上山岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步子飞跃胳膊闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百凤朝阳展翅膀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪上肩，枪下肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装子弹，退子弹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看她们练得多带劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看她们练得多熟练！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘巧，巧姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽肩膀，红脸膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕耩锄刨是行家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练兵场上英雄将。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地头操练"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵哨响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦田里燕子飞翔；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声口令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民兵排成一道道人墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人墙里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀闪亮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映着英雄的脸庞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男民兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头系白毛巾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女民兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辫子缠在脖子上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步子走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地发抖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀声喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天摇晃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵阵歌声一阵阵笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪声飞散头昂扬……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖上渔歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只燕子点水过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两把船桨戏水波；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑嫂二人去捕鱼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一船笑声一湖歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群大雁湖边过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘用手跟嫂说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂放桨拿起枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪声响处大雁落。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪声响处大雁落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雁落处笑脸多；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子齐夸枪法好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂脸上泛红波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘才要夸哥哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂拨船箭飞梭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你这个丫头甭多嘴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知道你爱民兵连的好小伙！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘撒网唱渔歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂支篙掌住舵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支渔歌一网银，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船上银鲤上了箩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只燕子点水过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两把船桨戏水波；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑嫂渔船回食堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一船笑声一湖歌……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}